<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Lupa Password - SIPANDI</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/output.css">
</head>

<body
    class="bg-gradient-to-br from-sipandi-green-50 to-sipandi-green-100 min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-4">
    <div class="card max-w-md w-full bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-8">
            <div class="flex justify-center mb-6">
                <div class="bg-sipandi-green-100 p-4 rounded-full shadow-inner">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"
                        stroke="currentColor" class="w-10 h-10 text-sipandi-green-600">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                            d="M16.5 10.5V6.75a4.5 4.5 0 1 0-9 0v3.75m-.75 11.25h10.5a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25-2.25v-6.75a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25-2.25H6.75a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25 2.25v6.75a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 2.25Z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-sipandi-green-700 mb-2">Lupa Password</h1>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Masukkan alamat email yang terdaftar, kami akan mengirimkan kode OTP untuk
                melanjutkan proses pemulihan akun Anda.</p>
        </div>

        <% if (error) { %>
            <div class="bg-red-100 border border-red-400 text-red-700 px-4 py-3 rounded-lg mb-4" role="alert">
                <span>
                    <%= error %>
                </span>
            </div>
            <% } %>

                <form action="/forgot-password" method="POST" class="space-y-4">
                    <div>
                        <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Email</label>
                        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required class="input-field"
                            placeholder="nama@email.com">
                    </div>

                    <button type="submit" class="btn-primary w-full">
                        Kirim OTP
                    </button>
                </form>

                <div class="mt-6 text-center">
                    <a href="/login" class="text-sm text-sipandi-green-600 hover:text-sipandi-green-700 font-semibold">
                        Kembali ke Login
                    </a>
                </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>